cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with image filtering, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of gradient descent to learn filter parameters is a machine learning technique (cs.LG). The application of the learned pairwise potentials to image segmentation tasks involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposal of bilateral neural networks is a novel approach to neural networks, which falls under the category of neural engineering (cs.NE). Finally, the experiments conducted in the paper involve the evaluation of different models, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
